import fs from"fs-promise";import Promise from"bluebird";import path from"path";import chalk from"chalk";import{biomeFolderName}from"./constants";export default function ls(){return fs.readdir(biomeFolderName()).then(e=>{console.info(`(for help, run ${chalk.green("biome --help")})`),console.info(`(use ${chalk.green("biome init [project]")} to create a new project)`),console.info(`(use ${chalk.green("biome use <name>")} to activate)`),console.info("All biomes:"),e.forEach(e=>{let o=e.replace(/\.json$/,"");console.info(process.env.BIOME_PROJECT&&process.env.BIOME_PROJECT.trim()===o.trim()?chalk.red("*"):" ",o)})})}